exposed in API responses."}}, "aboutDescription": "Connect your Linear account to Twenty to create issues and look up teams straight from your workflows or the AI chat.\\n\\n## What you can do\\n\\nOnce installed and connected, two tools become available:\\n\\n- **Create Linear issue**\\n  - From the AI chat, ask something like *\\"create a Linear issue in the Engineering team titled 'Fix login bug'\\"* and the AI will file it for you.\\n  - From a workflow, add it as a step with `teamId` + `title` (and optional `description`).\\n\\n- **List Linear teams** — discovers the teams in your Linear workspace, useful when you need to pick a `teamId` for the create-issue step.\\n\\n## Installing\\n\\n1. Open **Settings → Applications** in your Twenty workspace.\\n2. Find **Linear** in the available apps and click **Install**.\\n3. Open the app, go to the **Connections** tab, and click **Add connection**.\\n4. Choose **Just for me** (your personal Linear account) or **Workspace shared** (a team-managed Linear account anyone in this workspace can act through), then complete the Linear sign-in.\\n\\nThat's it — you can now use the tools above.", "yarnLockChecksum": "ded5f315e47053806dbea38b3da1c9c7", "packageJsonChecksum": "44719a61d0ef573dabde0b2d88855e4d", "universalIdentifier": "6f4e7c2a-3d8e-4a91-b2cf-9e0b8d5f4a2e", "defaultRoleUniversalIdentifier": "b6c33347-e41c-4b90-8a37-7b3c49baa85a"}, "pageLayouts": [], "publicAssets": [{"checksum": "b3b35a3427b1a69ffecbe3d605a7a16f", "fileName": "command-menu-item-1.png", "filePath": "public/gallery/command-menu-item-1.png", "fileType": "png"}, {"checksum": "6ad01cca1da31e2e7e7fcdeb56f5a583", "fileName": "command-menu-item-2.png", "filePath": "public/gallery/command-menu-item-2.png", "fileType": "png"}, {"checksum": "dd5d47ef4a45c5f5f68c666bf4996f5c", "fileName": "command-menu-item-3.png", "filePath": "public/gallery/command-menu-item-3.png", "fileType": "png"}, {"checksum": "61c47ed83754f9c6f050fe1810bbc38f", "fileName": "command-menu-item-4.png", "filePath": "public/gallery/command-menu-item-4.png", "fileType": "png"}, {"checksum": "7a0a408325d1b625a7c015b8979752a9", "fileName": "linear-logomark.svg", "filePath": "public/linear-logomark.svg", "fileType": "svg"}], "logicFunctions": [{"name": "create-linear-issue", "description": "Create a Linear issue on behalf of the connected user. Requires a teamId (call list-linear-teams to discover one) and a title.", "handlerName": "default.config.handler", "timeoutSeconds": 30, "builtHandlerPath": "src/logic-functions/create-linear-issue.mjs", "sourceHandlerPath": "src/logic-functions/create-linear-issue.ts", "toolTriggerSettings": {"inputSchema": {"type": "object", "required": ["teamId", "title"], "properties": {"title": {"type": "string", "description": "The issue title."}, "teamId": {"type": "string", "description": "The Linear team ID to create the issue in. Use list-linear-teams to discover available teams."}, "cycleId": {"type": "string", "description": "The cycle ID to add the issue to."}, "dueDate": {"type": "string", "description": "Due date in YYYY-MM-DD format."}, "stateId": {"type": "string", "description": "The workflow state ID for the issue status. Use list-linear-issue-options to discover available states for a team."}, "estimate": {"type": "number", "description": "The estimate value for the issue. Must match the team estimate scale."}, "labelIds": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "string"}, "description": "Array of label IDs to apply to the issue."}, "priority": {"type": "integer", "maximum": 4, "minimum": 0, "description": "Issue priority: 0 = No priority, 1 = Urgent, 2 = High, 3 = Medium, 4 = Low."}, "projectId": {"type": "string", "description": "The project ID to associate the issue with."}, "assigneeId": {"type": "string", "description": "The user ID to assign the issue to. Use list-linear-issue-options to discover team members."}, "description": {"type": "string", "description": "Optional issue description (Markdown supported)